20South%20African%20rand%20(about%20%241%2C500%20USD).%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHowever%2C%20the%20gift%20came%20with%20the%20condition%20that%20I%20see%20a%20financial%20advisor%20and%20invest%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI'm%20grateful%20both%20for%20the%20gift%20and%20for%20what%20it%20taught%20me.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20month%20before%20my%2021st%20birthday%2C%20my%20grandfather%20told%20me%20he%20would%20be%20gifting%20me%2021%2C000%20South%20African%20rand%20(approximately%20%241%2C500%20USD%20based%20on%20the%20exchange%20rate%20at%20the%20time).%20However%2C%20there%20was%20a%20catch%3A%20I%20had%20to%20visit%20a%20financial%20advisor%20with%20him%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fhow-to-buy-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvest%20the%20money%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20I%20valued%20the%20freedom%20that%20money%20gave%20me%2C%20but%20I%20had%20given%20little%20consideration%20to%20investing.%20I%20had%20been%20working%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flaid-off-from-corporate-job-lessons-learned-bartending-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epart-time%20bar%20job%3C%2Fa%3E%20throughout%20university%2C%20I%20took%20on%20promoting%20gigs%20whenever%20possible%2C%20and%20I%20was%20just%20starting%20to%20get%20freelance%20writing%20gigs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20my%20earned%20money%20went%20toward%20subsidizing%20my%20lifestyle%20in%20university%20(usually%20drunken%20nights%20out%20or%20greasy%20takeaways%20from%20the%20local%20pizza%20shop)%2C%20or%20I%20saved%20the%20money%20for%20a%20specific%20occasion%2C%20like%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwent-on-road-trip-new-partner-year-into-relationship-lessons-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eroad%20trip%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20my%20roommate%20across%20the%20country.%20That%20said%2C%20I%20welcomed%20the%2021st%20birthday%20gift%2C%20and%20I%20knew%20that%20it%20was%20something%20I'd%20grow%20to%20appreciate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2224ef559c-3c8e-44ac-95f0-623774742219%5C%22%3EI%20knew%20investing%20was%20responsible%2C%20but%20I%20also%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20future%20priority%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20early%202019%2C%20six%20months%20after%20my%2021st%20birthday%2C%20my%20grandpa%20set%20up%20an%20appointment%20for%20me%20to%20meet%20my%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-does-a-financial-advisor-do%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinancial%20advisor%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20sat%20in%20a%20boardroom%20as%20my%20financial%20advisor%20explained%20stocks%20and%20the%20market%2C%20throwing%20around%20terms%20that%20went%20completely%20over%20my%20head%2C%20such%20as%20%26quot%3Brepo%20rate%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BCapital%20Gains%20Tax%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bvolatility.%26quot%3B%20I%20nodded%20along%2C%20hoping%20it%20looked%20like%20I%20understood%20more%20than%20I%20did.%20My%20grandfather%20would%20occasionally%20ask%20my%20advisor%20to%20explain%20important%20concepts%2C%20such%20as%20highlighting%20the%20risks%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fearly-401k-withdrawals-hardship-distributions-retirement-funds-investing-advice-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewithdrawing%20the%20money%20too%20soon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20especially%20when%20the%20market%20was%20in%20a%20bad%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20we%20set%20the%20investment%20up%2C%20I%20received%20quarterly%20updates%20via%20email.%20I%20rarely%20opened%20them%2C%20and%20I%20almost%20forgot%20all%20about%20the%20investment%20portfolio.%20However%2C%20during%20a%20family%20Easter%20holiday%20two%20years%20after%20setting%20up%20the%20portfolio%2C%20the%20topic%20of%20investments%20came%20up.%20My%20brother%20asked%20me%20how%20much%20my%20portfolio%20had%20grown%20(my%20grandfather%20had%20set%20up%20something%20similar%20for%20him%2C%20too).%20I%20opened%20my%20email%20to%20check%3A%20The%20balance%20was%2028%2C138%20ZAR.%20This%20was%20a%2034%25%20increase%20in%20just%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20this%20time%2C%20I%20had%20graduated%20from%20university%2C%20and%20I%20was%20starting%20to%20earn%20a%20decent%20amount%20of%20money%20in%20my%20PR%20business.%20I%20was%20still%20unsure%20about%20how%20taxes%20worked%2C%20so%20I%20was%20overestimating%20the%20amount%20of%20money%20to%20put%20aside%20for%20them%20each%20month.%20However%2C%20in%202022%2C%20after%20hiring%20a%20tax%20consultant%20and%20filing%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ftaxes%2Fhow-to-file-taxes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannual%20tax%20returns%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20discovered%20that%20I%20had%20a%20good%20chunk%20of%20money%20left%20in%20savings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20and%20her%20grandfather.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F695d816b64858d02d217de6a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20learned%20a%20lot%20about%20finances%20from%20her%20grandfather.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Alice%20Draper%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222c871404-622c-4d23-8407-a54ace781e4a%5C%22%3EThree%20years%20after%20starting%20the%20investment%2C%20I%20added%20to%20the%20portfolio%20myself%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20remembered%20the%20investment%20my%20grandfather%20helped%20me%20set%20up%2C%20and%20I%20emailed%20my%20financial%20advisor%2C%20asking%20whether%20I%20could%20add%20an%20additional%2080%2C000%20South%20African%20rand%20to%20the%20portfolio.%20We%20set%20this%20up%2C%20and%20I%20also%20inquired%20about%20retirement%2C%20arranging%20a%20monthly%20debit%20order%20that%20would%20go%20to%20my%20tax-free%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fbest-retirement-plans%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eretirement%20fund%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20grandfather%20did%20not%20merely%20gift%20me%20capital%3B%20he%20gave%20me%20the%20gift%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinancial-literacy-young-earned-credit-card-debt-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinancial%20literacy%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20knew%20that%20the%20best%20way%20for%20me%20to%20understand%20the%20value%20of%20investing%20was%20to%20see%20my%20own%20money%20grow.%20I%20am%20lucky%20to%20still%20have%20him%20around%20as%20a%20mentor%2C%20and%20I%20often%20ask%20him%20for%20financial%20(and%20business)%20advice.%20His%20approach%20is%20never%20prescriptive%3B%20in%20fact%2C%20even%20at%2021%2C%20he%20never%20told%20me%20that%20I%20had%20to%20keep%20my%20money%20with%20a%20financial%20advisor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20my%20grandfather%20has%20always%20believed%20that%20equipping%20people%20with%20options%20through%20knowledge%2C%20tools%2C%20or%20resources%20creates%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20security.%20Learning%20to%20invest%20at%2021%20gave%20me%20exactly%20that%3A%20the%20ability%20to%20make%20thoughtful%20choices%20with%20my%20money%20as%20my%20life%20and%20income%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrandfather-financial-advisor-investment-account-birthday-present-2026-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1767872461000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F695d809564858d02d217de42%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrandfather-financial-advisor-investment-account-birthday-present-2026-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20I%20turned%2021%2C%20my%20grandfather%20gave%20me%20money%20as%20long%20as%20I%20see%20a%20financial%20advisor%20with%20him%20and%20invest.%20It'