oint%20operation%20like%20that%20is%20really%20quite%20difficult%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESetting%20up%20a%20cyber%20operation%20like%20this%2C%20she%20explained%2C%20%26quot%3Bwould%20have%20taken%20quite%20a%20long%20time%20and%20an%20incredible%20skill%20level%20in%20order%20to%20make%20all%20those%20pieces%20come%20together%20at%20the%20right%20moment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20put%20months%20of%20planning%20into%20this%20operation%2C%20opening%20up%20a%20mix%20of%20possibilities.%20Olejnik%20said%20it%20%26quot%3Bwould%20not%20be%20too%20difficult%26quot%3B%20for%20American%20forces%20to%20shut%20off%20the%20power%20given%20the%20time%20available%20to%20prep%20for%20this%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20sufficient%20to%20build%20the%20capability%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20brought%20significant%20airpower%20into%20this%20operation%2C%20along%20with%20a%20deeply%20capable%20cyber%20force%2C%20pitting%20that%20against%20Venezuelan%20infrastructure%20that%20has%20been%20in%20crisis%20for%20years%20amid%20the%20country's%20political%20and%20financial%20issues.%20It%20has%20resulted%20in%20blackouts%20and%20various%20other%20service%20interruptions%20without%20external%20interference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOlejnik%20said%20Venezuela's%20long-standing%20infrastructure%20troubles%20are%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20relevant%26quot%3B%20to%20what%20the%20US%20may%20have%20done%20there.%20%26quot%3BThe%20infrastructure%20and%20power%20grids%20are%20both%20less%20complex%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20some%20of%20them%20may%20contain%20outdated%20hardware%20and%20software.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGaudette%20described%20Venezuela's%20cybersecurity%20and%20cyberspace%20situation%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20very%20porous%20environment%2C%20very%20open%2C%20very%20susceptible%20to%20attack%20if%20the%20United%20States%20were%20to%20choose%20to%20go%20that%20route.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20shared%20that%20he%20suspects%20the%20US%20may%20have%20gone%20with%20a%20simple%20attack%20rather%20than%20a%20deeply%20complex%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20a%20state%20actor%20would%20take%20the%20path%20of%20least%20resistance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20unless%20it%20just%20wanted%20to%20test%20out%20a%20new%20capability.%20While%20possible%2C%20Gaudette%20suggested%20the%20US%20would%20likely%20not%20want%20to%20%26quot%3Bburn%20a%20high-end%20capability%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20mission%20like%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20blackened%20and%20charred%20piece%20of%20weaponry%20under%20some%20trees%20with%20some%20cars%20behind%20it%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F695e5469832e0ef1ead7503d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20destroyed%20anti-aircraft%20unit%20at%20La%20Carlota%20military%20air%20base%20after%20the%20US%20operation%20in%20Venezuela.%3Cp%3ELeonardo%20Fernandez%20Viloria%2FREUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20manufactured%20darkness%20plays%20to%20US%20strengths%2C%20especially%20for%20this%20type%20of%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarding%2C%20who%20previously%20held%20multiple%20national%20security%20positions%2C%20including%20at%20the%20CIA%20and%20National%20Security%20Council%2C%20said%20the%20US%20operates%20%26quot%3Bvery%20well%20in%20darkness%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20vast%20intelligence%20available%20meant%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20didn't%20need%20to%20see%20where%20we%20were%20going.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20all%20the%20technology%20we%20needed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20we%20had%20it%20all%20mapped%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2286fe41fe-b97d-4936-9fc7-1830030119e5%5C%22%3ELess%20obvious%20ways%20of%20war%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20US%20took%20action%20using%20cyberwarfare%2C%20it%20wouldn't%20be%20the%20first%20time%20that's%20be