%20biosphere%20is%20a%20result%20of%20Jai's%20search%20for%20clean%20air%20and%20pristine%20nature.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji3-1724833586.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji3-1724833586-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji3-1724833586-500x374.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji3-1724833586-768x575.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji3-1724833586-1536x1150.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji3-1724833586-150x112.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-363167%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221198%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20biosphere%20is%20a%20result%20of%20Jai%E2%80%99s%20search%20for%20clean%20air%20and%20pristine%20nature.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20he%20discovered%20a%20stunning%20piece%20of%20land%20nestled%20between%20the%20Rajaji%20Tiger%20Reserve%20and%20the%20Raghati%20river%2C%20complete%20with%20a%20breathtaking%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F338189%2Fbest-national-park-wildlife-safaris-in-winter-adventure-travel-guide-vacation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E300-metre-wide%20riverbed%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20riverbed%2C%20when%20dry%2C%20serves%20as%20an%20elephant%20corridor%20and%20a%20hub%20of%20wildlife%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20that%20being%20there%20feels%20like%20stepping%20into%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Jungle%20Book%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20where%20you%20can%20watch%20animals%20in%20their%20natural%20habitat%20%E2%80%94%20preying%2C%20drinking%2C%20sleeping%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20biosphere%2C%20he%20explains%2C%20is%20a%20micro-environment.