%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji4-1724833594-1536x1150.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji4-1724833594-150x112.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-363168%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221198%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20biosphere%20was%20created%20through%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%20of%20relentless%20effort.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJai%20and%20Vijay%20surveyed%20the%20nearby%20area%20of%20the%20Rajaji%20Tiger%20Reserve%20and%20National%20Park%20together%2C%20identifying%2062%20native%20tree%20species%20that%20were%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20disappearing.%20The%20project%20began%20with%20the%20collection%20of%20seeds%20and%20the%20painstaking%20process%20of%20planting%20saplings%20of%20these%20endangered%20species.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijay%2C%20who%20has%20been%20in%20the%20rewilding%20and%20wildlife%20restoration%20space%20for%20over%2020%20years%20and%20majorly%20works%20on%20government%20projects%2C%20had%20an%20interesting%20task%20up%20his%20sleeve.%20He%20states%20that%20there%20is%20just%20a%20wall%20that%20separates%20the%20biosphere%20from%20the%20Rajaji%20National%20Park.%20The%20idea%20was%20to%20get%20a%20slice%20of%20Rajaji%20into%20this%20land%2C%20which%20had%20been%20altered%20by%20humans%20for%20their%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20task%20was%20removing%20the%20eucalyptus%20trees.%20The%20second%20task%20was%20creating%20natural%20contours%20that%20existed%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20monsoon%20that%20I%20experienced%20was%20really%20horrifying.%20I%20found%20that%20the%20rainwater%20was%20tapering%20away%20towards%20the%20river.%20Nothing%20was%20being%20retained%20in%20the%20land.%20The%20rain%20was%20taking%20away%20my%20topsoil%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vijay%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20a%20war%20footing%2C%20we%20created%20the%20natural%20contours%20that%20existed%20to%20ensure%20that%20rainwater%20recharges%20our%20land.%20We%20are%20working%20on%20creating%20magic%2C%20every%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20how%20they%20worked%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F345145%2Fforest-officer-saves-trees-in-chhattisgarh-forest-tiger-reserve-from-encroachers-ifs-varun-jain-timber-poaching%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erewilding%20the%20land%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20says%20that%20they%20took%20cues%20from%20the%20forest%20next%20door.%20They%20observed%20the%20forest%20and%20the%20species%20that%20grew%20there%20and%20worked%20on%20recreating%20the%20broken%20linkages%20between%20different%20species%20and%20creating%20an%20interdependence%20between%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-33-1724828441.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22how%20to%20build%20a%20biosphere%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-33-1724828441.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-33-1724828441-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-33-1724828441-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-33-1724828441-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-33-1724828441-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-363141%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20Rajaji%20Raghati%20Biosphere%20is%20rich%20in%20biodiversity%20and%20home%20to%20132%20native%20plant%20species%2C%20including%20many%20that%20had%20all%20but%20disappeared%20from%20the%20region.%20Their%20efforts%20have%20also%20attracted%20a%20diverse%20array%20of%20wildlife%20%E2%80%94%20from%20leopards%20and%20elephants%20to%20an%20abundance%20of%20bird%20species%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20which%20are%20now%20regular%20visitors%20to%20the%20biosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20saplings%20are%20now%20about%20six%20feet%20high%2C%20and%20when%20you%20walk%2C%20you%20feel%20like%20you%E2%80%99re%20walking%20on%20a%20carpet.%20We%20have%20two%20leopards%20and%20elephants%20who%20visit%20regularly.%20Earlier%2C%20when%20they%20would%20come%20down%20the%20corridor%2C%20they%20would%20stop%20and%20show%20signs%20of%20being%20upset.%20Now%2C%20they%20look%20at%20me%20as%20a%20part%20of%20their%20habitat.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20realised%20that%20my%20vision%20of%20coexistence%20is%20coming%20true%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Uttarakhand%20biosphere%20reserve%20operates%20under%20strict%20rules%3A%20vehicles%20and%20plastic%20are%20not%20allowed.%20The%20only%20exception%20is%20a%20single%20electric%20farm%20utility%20vehicle%2C%20which%20also%20serves%20as%20a%20silent%20safari%20vehicle%2C%20ensuring%20minimal%20disturbance%20to%20the%20animals.%20Visitors%20are%20not%20permitted%20to%20bring%20any%20plants%20or%20seeds%20into%20the%20biosphere.%20Every%20effort%20is%20made%20to%20avoid%20activities%20that%20contribute%20to%20a%20carbon%20footprint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20rule%20in%20this%20biosphere%20is%20that%20nature%20comes%20first%2C%20not%20humans%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jai.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20small%20homes%20on%20the%20property%20for%20overnight%20stays%2C%20built%20without%20cement%20and%20bricks%2C%20using%20prefabricated%20construction%20methods.%20Jai%20emphasises%20that%20this%20is%20not%20an%20eco-tourism%20spot%20but%20rather%20a%20model%20intended%20to%20inspire%20others%20who%20wish%20to%20rewild%20their%20own%20spaces.%20He%20has%20also%20written%20a%20white%20paper%20on%20the%20subject%20to%20raise%20awareness%20and%20motivate%20others%20to%20take%20similar%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20already%20feel%20like%20the%20richest%20person%20on%20the%20planet.%20I%20have%20created%20more%20wealth%20over%20the%20past%202.5%20years%20than%20in%20the%2050%20years%20before%20that.%20One%20must%20realise%20that%20richness%20is%20not%20in%20our%2030%2C000%20sq%20ft%20mansions%20and%20apartments%20in%20cities.%20The%20richness%20lies%20in%20mental%20peace%2C%20which%20I%E2%80%99ve%20found.%20Most%20days%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20even%20walking%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20levitating%20in%20the%20biosphere%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijay%20too%20adds%20that%20he%20has%20received%20calls%20from%20people%20across%20the%20country%20interested%20in%20replicating%20this%20initiative.%20The%20message%20the%20duo%20want%20to%20give%20out%20is%20clear%20as%20day%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CLet%E2%80%99s%20go%20back%20to%20the%20simpler%20things%20and%20reconnect%20with%20nature.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EImages%20Courtesy%20Jai%20Dhar%20Gupta%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757331000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji2-1724829336.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D498044%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Inspired%20by%20the%20movie%20Avatar%2C%20environmentalist%20and%20clean%20air%20activist%20Jai%20Dhar%20Gupta%20turned%2032%20acres%20near%20Uttarakhand's%20Rajaji%20National%20Park%20into%20a%20biosphere.%20With%20the%20help%20of%20expert%20Vijay%20Dhasmana%2C%20he%20revived%20the%20land%2C%20bringing%20back%20native%20plants%20and%20wildlife.%